v2.title: Changelog
v2.description: New changes, updates and some notes!

fields.name: Changes
fields.value:
```diff
+ Bot Rename: Chemistry Utilities Fox -> Chemistry Fox
+ Added: Invite, Bugreport, Suggestion, Botinfo, Average, Vote, Constants
+ Improved Help Menu
+ New Select Menu and Buttons!
+ Improved bot replies by using embeds
+ Added links to PubChem for PubChem commands```

fields.name: Notes and Considerations
fields.value:
```diff
- Planning on adding more math commands, unsure what yet
- Adding more chemistry commands (solutions, hydrogen orbital energy, wavelength-frequency-energy calculations, electrolysis[seconds, amps, grams, element])
- Adding more Constants
- Attempted multi-language support, but unable to currently do it. Will try once again in the future
- Should I add a quiz feature + multiple answer question feature?```

footer.text: Reply to notes and Considerations by using the Suggestion command!
